Update package lists (always first):

----sudo apt update                                         # (recommended)


####Install pip3 (verbatim shown in PDF):

sudo apt install python3-pip                            # (from PDF)


#####Install OSRFramework (verbatim shown in PDF):

sudo pip3 install osrframework                          # (from PDF)


#######Clone Sublist3r (verbatim shown in PDF):

git clone https://github.com/aboul3la/sublist3r.git     # (from PDF)
cd sublist3r                                           # go into repo to run it
# run later with: python3 sublist3r.py -d target.com    # example usage (recommended)


###Run usufy and mailfy (verbatim shown in PDF):

sudo usufy -n cyberhia                                  # (from PDF) -- example
sudo mailfy -n cyberhia                                 # (from PDF) -- example


######3Use the common Google dorks (text to paste into Google; from PDF):

inurl:/wp-content/uploads/ ext.txt "username" AND "password" | "pwd" | "pw"
inurl:/proc/self/cwd
intitle:"index of" inurl:ftp
filetype:xls inurl:"email.xls"


(enter each dork in Google search box; these are provided in the PDF). 



#####Check breach sites (open in browser; links from PDF):

https://haveibeenpwned.com
https://haveibeenzuckered.com/


(visit in browser). 


#####3Wordlists location (reference):

/usr/share/wordlists                                   # (from PDF)
